<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="idefb13ed7-3a6e-11f1-addd-bbaf0b3f68e9" identifier="/us/usc/t7/s3811"><num value="3811">§ 3811.</num><heading> Issuance of regulations; maintenance of rec­ords</heading><content>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">The Secretary is authorized to issue such regulations and to require the maintenance of such records as he deems necessary to carry out the provisions of this chapter.</p>
</content><sourceCredit id="idefb13ed8-3a6e-11f1-addd-bbaf0b3f68e9">(<ref href="/us/pl/96/468/s11">Pub. L. 96–468, § 11</ref>, formerly § 12, <date date="1980-10-17">Oct. 17, 1980</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/94/2233">94 Stat. 2233</ref>; renumbered § 11, <ref href="/us/pl/104/127/tIX/s914/b/2">Pub. L. 104–127, title IX, § 914(b)(2)</ref>, <date date="1996-04-04">Apr. 4, 1996</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/110/1186">110 Stat. 1186</ref>.)</sourceCredit>
<notes type="uscNote" id="idefb13ed9-3a6e-11f1-addd-bbaf0b3f68e9">
<note style="-uslm-lc:I74" role="crossHeading" topic="editorialNotes" id="idefb13eda-3a6e-11f1-addd-bbaf0b3f68e9"><heading class="centered"><b>Editorial Notes</b></heading></note>
<note style="-uslm-lc:I74" topic="priorProvisions" id="idefb13edb-3a6e-11f1-addd-bbaf0b3f68e9"><heading class="centered smallCaps">Prior Provisions</heading><p style="-uslm-lc:I21" class="indent0">A prior <ref href="/us/pl/96/468/s11">section 11 of Pub. L. 96–468</ref> was classified to <ref href="/us/usc/t7/s3810">section 3810 of this title</ref> prior to repeal by <ref href="/us/pl/104/127">Pub. L. 104–127</ref>.</p>
</note>
</notes>
